 </div>	<div class="pub-bg">
		<div class="container news-details">
					<h1 class=" te_c">西藏民族大学附属医院进口高压注射器维修招标公告</h1>
					<div class="info te_c">
						<span>发布时间：2026-06-30</span>
						<span>浏览次数：<pageview id="0808e228-0d37-4906-824a-4103f4aaa2e6" >0</pageview><script type="text/javascript">$(function(){$.ajax({url: "/Server/Preview/callBack/News/PageView",type: "POST",data: {newsId:"0808e228-0d37-4906-824a-4103f4aaa2e6"},success: function(result) {if (result.success){$("#0808e228-0d37-4906-824a-4103f4aaa2e6").text(result.data.pageView);}}});});</script></span>
					</div>
					<div class="line p_r"></div>
					<div class="body">
						<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; line-height: 21.75pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">我院将就一</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">台进口高压注射器</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">进行</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">维修</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">，</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">招标</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">公告如下：</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">一、</span></strong><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">维修</span></strong><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">地点</span></strong></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">西藏民族大学附属医院新综合楼</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">影像科</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">。</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">二：产品概况：</span></strong><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></strong></p> 
<div style="text-indent: 2em;" align="center"> 
 <table class="MsoNormalTable" style="width: 464.25pt; border-image: initial; text-indent: 2em; border: medium none currentcolor;" border="1" cellspacing="0"> 
  <tbody style="text-indent: 2em;"> 
   <tr style="height: 23.1pt; text-indent: 2em;"> 
    <td style="width: 36.65pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border: 1pt solid #000000; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="48"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">序号</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 151.5pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: #000000 #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="202"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">产品</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">名称</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 33.75pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: #000000 #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="45"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">数量</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 33pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: #000000 #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="44"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">单位</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 209.35pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: 1pt 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: solid solid solid none; border-color: #000000 #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="279"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">情况说明</span></p> </td> 
   </tr> 
   <tr style="height: 37pt; text-indent: 2em;"> 
    <td style="width: 36.65pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor #000000 #000000; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="48"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">1</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 151.5pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentcolor #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="202"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">美瑞德（拜耳）高压注射器</span></p> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">SCT211</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 33.75pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentcolor #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="45"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">1</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 33pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentcolor #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="44"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">台</span></p> </td> 
    <td style="width: 209.35pt; padding: 0pt 5.4pt; border-width: medium 1pt 1pt medium; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: currentcolor #000000 #000000 currentcolor; text-indent: 2em;" valign="center" width="279"> <p class="p" style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;" align="center"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">高压注射器核心主控板、针筒传感器板</span></p> </td> 
   </tr> 
  </tbody> 
 </table> 
</div> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">二、</span></strong><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">投标</span></strong><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">要求</span></strong></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">1. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">维修公司需要提供原厂配件。</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin: 0pt 0pt 0pt 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">2. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">维修公司须具备</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">原厂对维修公司的授权、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">营业执照、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">医疗器械</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">备案凭证</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">、医疗器械经营许可</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">证、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">维修工程师应具备相应资质或经过原厂技术培训。</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">3. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">维修完成后，应对设备进行全面的功能测试和性能校准，确保各项性能指标达到或超过设备原有标准。</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">4. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">维修质量保证期：维修完成验收合格之日起，同一故障保修不低于</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">6个月。</span></span></p> 
<p class="18" style="margin-left: 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">5. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">质保期内如因维修质量问题或配件质量问题导致设备再次故障，维修公司应无偿进行修复，并承担由此产生的一切费用，包括但不限于配件费用、运输费用、人工费用等</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">。</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">6. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">维修公司应设立</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">24小时服务电话，提供技术支持。</span></span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">7. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">维修公司应在质保期内提供免费的售后技术服务，包括故障排查、技术咨询等。</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 21.25pt; line-height: 28.8pt; text-indent: 2em;"><!-- [if !supportLists]--><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">8. </span><!--[endif]--><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">维修公司应对维修后的设备进行定期回访，了解设备运行状况。</span></p> 
<p class="18" style="line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">三、报名要求：</span></strong></p> 
<p class="18" style="line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">1、报名时间（网上报名）：2026年</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">7</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1日起至2026年</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">7</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">月</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">7</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">日上午</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">11:30止。（上午：08:00—11:30，下午：14:00—17:30，节假日和非工作时间除外。）逾期将不再接收任何资料</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">。</span></p> 
<p class="18" style="line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">2、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">报名资料：</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">原厂对维修公司授权书、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">营业执照、医疗器械</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">备案凭证</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">、医疗器械经营许可、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">维修</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">公司对个人授权委托书、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">报价单等</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">资料一式</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">5份</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">并</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">加盖单位鲜章（</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">开标时</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">提交）。</span></p> 
<p class="18" style="line-height: 18pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">4、</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">上述资料需</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;">先</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 1.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">以</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">PDF格式于报名时间内发送至邮箱：</span></span><a href="mailto:1377663579@qq.com"><u><span class="16" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #0000ff; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">1377663579</span></span></u><u><span class="16" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #0000ff; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">@qq.</span></span></u><u><span class="16" style="font-family: 宋体; color: #0000ff; font-size: 11pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">com</span></span></u></a></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">开标时间及地点</span></strong></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">1.开标时间：202</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">6</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">年</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">7</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;"><span style="font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;">7日15:00</span></span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">2.开标地点：西藏民族大学附属医院综合楼</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><strong><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; mso-ansi-font-weight: bold; font-size: 11.0000pt;">四、联系方式</span></strong><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">&nbsp;</span></p> 
<p class="p" style="margin-left: 0pt; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">联系人：</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">文老师</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;联系电话：</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">029-</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 11.0000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt;">33757556</span></p>
					</div>
